The Japanese who came to our school yesterday

301
00:17:14,599 --> 00:17:15,930
were all burnt to death!

302
00:17:16,280 --> 00:17:17,000
Is that real?

303
00:17:17,000 --> 00:17:17,720
Really?

304
00:17:18,560 --> 00:17:19,240
Let me see.

305
00:17:19,240 --> 00:17:20,079
What's that?

306
00:17:20,920 --> 00:17:21,880
What happened?

307
00:17:22,280 --> 00:17:23,339
Ji Jin, read it out!

308
00:17:24,160 --> 00:17:27,480
The Japanese arsonist and his twenty-one fellows

309
00:17:27,720 --> 00:17:29,440
were all burnt to death.

310
00:17:33,840 --> 00:17:35,680
Who did this? When? Where?

311
00:17:36,120 --> 00:17:36,880
Ji Jin,

312
00:17:36,880 --> 00:17:38,160
does it answer these?

313
00:17:38,800 --> 00:17:40,000
Wait, let me check it.

314
00:17:41,040 --> 00:17:42,080
It doesn't say.

315
00:17:43,680 --> 00:17:44,560
But it's the Minduo Newspaper

316
00:17:44,560 --> 00:17:45,920
and it is written by Zhang Yuzhi.

317
00:17:45,920 --> 00:17:46,840
It must be true.

318
00:17:47,000 --> 00:17:48,000
It can't be wrong.

319
00:17:48,200 --> 00:17:49,800
Now it's spreading outside.

320
00:17:49,920 --> 00:17:51,320
Less than ten miles out of the city,

321
00:17:51,320 --> 00:17:52,480
on the way to Wangzhuang,

322
00:17:52,480 --> 00:17:53,640
the Japanese in the car

323
00:17:53,640 --> 00:17:54,970
were all burnt to ashes.

324
00:17:55,480 --> 00:17:57,120
Today's newspapers have been sold out.

325
00:17:57,120 --> 00:17:57,880
This one

326
00:17:57,880 --> 00:17:58,600
is borrowed from the

327
00:17:58,600 --> 00:17:59,530
entrance guard.

328
00:17:59,800 --> 00:18:00,660
Don't break it.

329
00:18:01,720 --> 00:18:03,180
They burned our students,

330
00:18:03,240 --> 00:18:05,770
and now they have become charcoal in the fire.

331
00:18:06,080 --> 00:18:07,200
God bless us!

332
00:18:07,200 --> 00:18:08,160
Screw it!

333
00:18:08,640 --> 00:18:09,800
If the God really blessed us,

334
00:18:09,800 --> 00:18:11,560
the students wouldn't have been killed.

335
00:18:11,560 --> 00:18:12,320
I think,

336
00:18:12,480 --> 00:18:14,010
this must be done by someone

337
00:18:14,440 --> 00:18:15,570
who was chivalrous.

338
00:18:16,400 --> 00:18:17,200
That's right.

339
00:18:17,440 --> 00:18:18,680
I wonder who did this.

340
00:18:18,880 --> 00:18:20,200
He must be a hero!

341
00:18:20,440 --> 00:18:20,960
Ji Jin.

342
00:18:21,120 --> 00:18:22,000
Give us the newspaper.

343
00:18:22,000 --> 00:18:23,200
We want to read it too.

344
00:18:23,560 --> 00:18:24,720
Don't snatch!

345
00:18:25,040 --> 00:18:25,880
I borrowed it!

346
00:18:25,880 --> 00:18:27,280
Be careful!

347
00:18:30,040 --> 00:18:30,480
Yes.

348
00:18:31,040 --> 00:18:31,560
Yes.

349
00:18:32,120 --> 00:18:33,200
It's all my fault.

350
00:18:46,360 --> 00:18:47,400
Anybody?

351
00:18:50,320 --> 00:18:50,680
Sir.

352
00:18:50,680 --> 00:18:52,560
Go call Lord Chengrui.

353
00:18:52,840 --> 00:18:54,000
I want to meet him.

354
00:18:54,600 --> 00:18:55,160
Yes, sir.

355
00:18:55,440 --> 00:18:57,160
Kazuo Sato is here.

356
00:19:54,320 --> 00:19:55,520
That's all for today.

357
00:19:55,720 --> 00:19:56,780
You can go home now.

358
00:20:04,840 --> 00:20:05,680
What for?

359
00:20:05,920 --> 00:20:06,640
Lord,

360
00:20:07,120 --> 00:20:08,720
Kazuo Sato from Japanese COC

361
00:20:08,720 --> 00:20:09,720
wants to see you.

362
00:20:10,000 --> 00:20:11,260
He is waiting outside.

363
00:20:16,800 --> 00:20:17,840
How ironic.

364
00:20:19,600 --> 00:20:21,730
Now a business man from a small country

365
00:20:22,160 --> 00:20:23,600
can see me at will.

366
00:20:24,560 --> 00:20:27,080
He said he had reasons.

367
00:20:31,120 --> 00:20:32,840
Tell him I'm not comfortable.

368
00:20:33,320 --> 00:20:35,250
I can't deal with other things now.

369
00:20:36,120 --> 00:20:37,480
My lord, your medicine.

370
00:20:39,960 --> 00:20:40,720
Too bitter!

371
00:20:41,600 --> 00:20:42,730
You take this for me.

372
00:20:43,000 --> 00:20:44,080
Let me help you.

373
00:20:46,200 --> 00:20:48,460
It's more bitter to drink spoon by spoon.

374
00:21:11,800 --> 00:21:13,240
Go find out who did that.

375
00:21:16,440 --> 00:21:17,400
Kazuo Sato said

376
00:21:18,080 --> 00:21:19,210
it was Shen Tingbai.

377
00:21:20,480 --> 00:21:21,600
Don't be so sure.

378
00:21:23,240 --> 00:21:25,240
The Japanese are so hated.

379
00:21:26,800 --> 00:21:30,000
Almost all the people want to kill them.

380
00:21:30,320 --> 00:21:31,080
Right.

381
00:21:32,480 --> 00:21:33,400
Besides,

382
00:21:33,720 --> 00:21:34,980
Ms. Xianrong was back.

383
00:21:40,080 --> 00:21:41,210
When did she arrive?

384
00:21:42,160 --> 00:21:44,240
I just got the information

385
00:21:44,640 --> 00:21:46,370
that she has arrived in Peking.

386
00:21:47,120 --> 00:21:48,320
Why did she come back?

387
00:21:48,440 --> 00:21:51,000
She is Hideyuki Oda's daughter.

388
00:21:51,560 --> 00:21:54,160
And Kazuo Sato is the retainer of Hideyuki Oda.

389
00:21:55,000 --> 00:21:57,660
Now Kazuo Sato has messed things up in Shunyuan.

390
00:21:57,800 --> 00:21:59,160
Maybe Ms. Xianrong

391
00:21:59,560 --> 00:22:00,480
is back to

392
00:22:00,920 --> 00:22:02,480
replace him now.

393
00:22:03,160 --> 00:22:04,640
So that's another reason

394
00:22:05,480 --> 00:22:07,360
why Mr. Sato wants to see you now.

395
00:22:10,200 --> 00:22:11,000
Beware of it.

396
00:22:11,880 --> 00:22:13,680
Tell me if she arrives in Shunyuan.

397
00:22:13,680 --> 00:22:14,240
Yes.

398
00:22:14,240 --> 00:22:14,960
Go now.

399
00:22:35,720 --> 00:22:37,240
Sorry, Mr. Sato.

400
00:22:37,560 --> 00:22:39,000
Lord feels unwell

401
00:22:39,400 --> 00:22:40,600
and doesn't meet visitors.

402
00:22:40,600 --> 00:22:41,840
Please go back.

403
00:23:26,600 --> 00:23:27,280
Well,

404
00:23:27,960 --> 00:23:28,640
excuse me.

405
00:23:29,400 --> 00:23:30,660
Are you looking for me?

406
00:23:38,680 --> 00:23:39,480
Jin Xianrong?

407
00:23:39,920 --> 00:23:40,850
Why are you here?

408
00:23:43,000 --> 00:23:44,080
Why can't I be here?

409
00:23:45,120 --> 00:23:46,180
Are you surprised?

410
00:23:46,720 --> 00:23:47,600
Sure.

411
00:23:48,080 --> 00:23:50,140
I was confused when my classmate said

412
00:23:50,240 --> 00:23:51,970
there was a girl looking for me.

413
00:23:54,560 --> 00:23:56,480
What do you think Shen Junshan

414
00:23:56,480 --> 00:23:57,810
has to do with that girl?

415
00:23:59,480 --> 00:24:00,940
That girl is so beautiful.

416
00:24:01,560 --> 00:24:02,480
I think

417
00:24:02,720 --> 00:24:04,320
their relationship must be special.

418
00:24:04,320 --> 00:24:05,450
When did you arrive?

419
00:24:05,720 --> 00:24:06,360
Not long.

420
00:24:07,240 --> 00:24:08,240
I came to see you

421
00:24:08,480 --> 00:24:10,080
as soon as I arrived in China.

422
00:24:11,400 --> 00:24:12,330
Are you touched?

423
00:24:19,200 --> 00:24:20,200
I remembered that

424
00:24:20,720 --> 00:24:22,320
you were studying medicine.

425
00:24:23,200 --> 00:24:23,840
Why do you

426
00:24:24,440 --> 00:24:25,800
turn to be a soldier?

427
00:24:29,720 --> 00:24:30,400
Junshan,

428
00:24:31,720 --> 00:24:32,920
you've changed a lot.

429
00:24:35,320 --> 00:24:36,600
You too.

430
00:24:39,240 --> 00:24:40,720
Why are we

431
00:24:40,800 --> 00:24:42,460
still standing here talking?

432
00:24:44,080 --> 00:24:45,040
What do you want to eat?

433
00:24:45,040 --> 00:24:46,500
Choose whatever you like.

434
00:24:47,320 --> 00:24:48,920
Then I have to think about it.

435
00:24:52,040 --> 00:24:52,600
Ji Jin,

436
00:24:53,040 --> 00:24:54,480
you are Junshan's best friend.

437
00:24:54,480 --> 00:24:55,480
What do you think?

438
00:24:56,800 --> 00:24:57,840
I don't know.

439
00:24:58,480 --> 00:25:01,080
But I know that Junshan studied in Britain before.

440
00:25:01,080 --> 00:25:03,740
Judging from the girl's dress and temperament,

441
00:25:04,160 --> 00:25:07,090
she should be his former classmate in Great Britain.

442
00:25:07,880 --> 00:25:09,000
Classmate?

443
00:25:09,720 --> 00:25:10,880
Then we still

444
00:25:11,400 --> 00:25:12,440
have the chance.

445
00:25:13,760 --> 00:25:15,020
Let's go and say hello.

446
00:25:16,040 --> 00:25:17,040
Why?

447
00:25:18,480 --> 00:25:19,160
Look,

448
00:25:19,440 --> 00:25:21,300
we are Junshan's classmates now.

449
00:25:21,920 --> 00:25:23,240
Now his friend is here,

450
00:25:23,880 --> 00:25:25,680
we should go and say hello to her.

451
00:25:26,880 --> 00:25:27,720
Yes.

452
00:25:27,840 --> 00:25:29,680
You should also treat her to dinner

453
00:25:29,680 --> 00:25:30,920
to do the honors.

454
00:25:30,920 --> 00:25:32,360
And ask her about age,

455
00:25:32,360 --> 00:25:33,040
family,

456
00:25:33,040 --> 00:25:34,440
and boyfriend by the way.

457
00:25:36,320 --> 00:25:37,080
Ji Jin,

458
00:25:37,400 --> 00:25:40,160
I don't think he has any female friend.

459
00:25:41,400 --> 00:25:42,760
I never saw her.

460
00:25:43,400 --> 00:25:44,530
It's the first time.

461
00:25:57,000 --> 00:25:57,860
How is the food?

462
00:26:01,280 --> 00:26:02,240
It's good.

463
00:26:03,360 --> 00:26:04,040
Junshan.

464
00:26:06,000 --> 00:26:06,680
Tingbai!

465
00:26:11,840 --> 00:26:12,770
You are here too.

466
00:26:14,280 --> 00:26:15,320
This is?

467
00:26:16,240 --> 00:26:18,840
This is my classmate in Britain, Jin Xianrong.

468
00:26:19,080 --> 00:26:21,080
This is my elder brother, Shen Tingbai.

469
00:26:21,080 --> 00:26:23,520
And this is his fiancee, Qu Manting.

470
00:26:24,960 --> 00:26:26,420
Hey, stop making fun of me.

471
00:26:26,520 --> 00:26:27,920
I'm not his fiancÃ©e

472
00:26:30,520 --> 00:26:31,240
Aren't you?

473
00:26:31,240 --> 00:26:32,360
Sure, I'm not.

474
00:26:33,080 --> 00:26:33,880
Fine.

475
00:26:34,680 --> 00:26:36,280
This is Ms. Qu Manting,

476
00:26:37,680 --> 00:26:39,400
not my brother's fiancee.

477
00:26:40,120 --> 00:26:41,200
Screw you!

478
00:26:41,760 --> 00:26:42,600
Ms. Jin,

479
00:26:42,960 --> 00:26:43,890
nice to meet you.

480
00:26:43,920 --> 00:26:45,280
Nice to meet you, Mr. Shen.

481
00:26:45,280 --> 00:26:46,740
I've heard a lot about you.

482
00:26:46,920 --> 00:26:48,280
How do you know me

483
00:26:49,120 --> 00:26:50,720
when you just arrived in China?

484
00:26:50,720 --> 00:26:51,960
My father and brother

485
00:26:51,960 --> 00:26:53,560
are doing business in China.

486
00:26:53,800 --> 00:26:55,440
They often mentioned you.

487
00:26:56,720 --> 00:26:58,040
I wonder who they are?

488
00:26:58,280 --> 00:27:00,400
They used to live in Peking

489
00:27:00,520 --> 00:27:02,050
and just moved to Shunyuan.

490
00:27:02,560 --> 00:27:04,640
You must not know them.

491
00:27:06,520 --> 00:27:07,640
What a pity.

492
00:27:08,520 --> 00:27:09,440
It doesn't matter.

493
00:27:09,440 --> 00:27:10,370
I'm in China now.

494
00:27:11,160 --> 00:27:13,800
There will be many chances for us to meet.

495
00:27:15,880 --> 00:27:16,560
Well,

496
00:27:16,920 --> 00:27:18,250
come and visit my family

497
00:27:18,720 --> 00:27:20,160
whenever you have time.

498
00:27:22,080 --> 00:27:23,720
I'm Junshan's friend.

499
00:27:24,200 --> 00:27:26,080
You don't need to call me Ms. Jin.

500
00:27:26,400 --> 00:27:28,040
Just call me Xianrong.

501
00:27:29,360 --> 00:27:31,490
Then don't call me Mr. Shen from now on.

502
00:27:31,760 --> 00:27:32,880
Just call me Tingbai

503
00:27:32,880 --> 00:27:33,940
like Junshan does.

504
00:27:35,960 --> 00:27:36,820
Okay, Tingbai.

505
00:27:38,920 --> 00:27:39,800
So Mr. Shen

506
00:27:40,520 --> 00:27:41,560
and Ms. Jin,

507
00:27:42,000 --> 00:27:43,120
are we done here?

508
00:27:44,000 --> 00:27:45,930
I got something to do. See you soon.

509
00:27:46,640 --> 00:27:47,500
Let me walk you.

510
00:27:48,000 --> 00:27:48,760
Sorry.

511
00:27:49,000 --> 00:27:50,330
Then we're leaving now.

512
00:27:50,680 --> 00:27:51,480
Bye.

513
00:27:51,480 --> 00:27:52,340
Don't touch me!

514
00:27:53,280 --> 00:27:54,040
See you.

515
00:27:59,800 --> 00:28:00,400
Xianrong,

516
00:28:01,280 --> 00:28:01,940
have a seat.

517
00:28:09,600 --> 00:28:10,720
Ms. Qu

518
00:28:11,720 --> 00:28:13,650
doesn't seem to like your brother.

519
00:28:15,160 --> 00:28:16,290
That will be better.

520
00:28:16,680 --> 00:28:18,010
I don't like her either.

521
00:28:20,680 --> 00:28:22,880
But your brother seems to like her a lot.

522
00:28:28,880 --> 00:28:30,000
Love is a thing

523
00:28:30,600 --> 00:28:32,320
that is easy to come and go.

524
00:28:33,600 --> 00:28:35,200
Especially one-sided love.

525
00:28:35,400 --> 00:28:36,460
It won't last long.

526
00:28:37,360 --> 00:28:38,560
My brother is smart.

527
00:28:39,080 --> 00:28:39,940
He will know it.

528
00:28:42,840 --> 00:28:44,700
You seem to understand love well.

529
00:28:47,200 --> 00:28:48,130
Isn't that true?

530
00:28:49,080 --> 00:28:51,010
This varies from person to person.

531
00:28:51,640 --> 00:28:53,200
The tougher the person,

532
00:28:53,800 --> 00:28:55,920
the more likely he is to be stubborn.

533
00:28:57,360 --> 00:28:59,360
Love is difficult to define.

534
00:29:16,400 --> 00:29:17,800
What are you laughing at?

535
00:29:19,120 --> 00:29:19,800
Nothing.

536
00:29:23,440 --> 00:29:25,480
Do you think I've changed a lot?

537
00:29:30,840 --> 00:29:32,500
Nearly four years have passed

538
00:29:33,120 --> 00:29:34,450
since the last meeting.

539
00:29:36,160 --> 00:29:36,840
Four years

540
00:29:39,040 --> 00:29:41,100
are enough to change someone's life.

541
00:29:42,760 --> 00:29:44,680
I hope you haven't changed so much.

542
00:29:44,680 --> 00:29:46,740
I like the Jin Xianrong you used to be.

543
00:29:50,320 --> 00:29:51,920
Then I have to think about

544
00:29:52,520 --> 00:29:54,650
what Jin Xianrong looked like before.

545
00:30:01,600 --> 00:30:03,800
How long are you going to stay this time?

546
00:30:06,000 --> 00:30:06,730
I don't know.

547
00:30:07,880 --> 00:30:09,080
I may stay a long time.

548
00:30:09,600 --> 00:30:11,130
There are many things to do.

549
00:30:13,640 --> 00:30:14,440
What are they?

550
00:30:16,400 --> 00:30:18,200
Business and personal affairs.

551
00:30:19,200 --> 00:30:19,920
Fine.

552
00:30:20,680 --> 00:30:22,400
Tell me if you need any help.

553
00:30:23,120 --> 00:30:23,720
Sure.

554
00:30:24,080 --> 00:30:25,840
You are my only friend in China.

555
00:30:27,320 --> 00:30:28,520
I'm happy to help you.

556
00:30:29,680 --> 00:30:31,400
And I will ask for your help if necessary.

557
00:30:31,400 --> 00:30:31,960
Cheers.

558
00:30:43,920 --> 00:30:45,120
Could I send you home?

559
00:30:45,720 --> 00:30:46,720
No. I didn't even see my family

560
00:30:46,720 --> 00:30:48,400
before I came to meet you.

561
00:30:48,680 --> 00:30:50,480
My family must be waiting for me.

562
00:30:50,880 --> 00:30:52,560
You can walk me home

563
00:30:52,880 --> 00:30:53,680
if you want to.

564
00:30:54,480 --> 00:30:56,140
But you should be responsible

565
00:30:56,440 --> 00:30:58,040
if they misunderstand that.

566
00:31:10,440 --> 00:31:11,320
It's coming.

567
00:31:19,040 --> 00:31:21,440
Don't think that I'm satisfied with only a meal.

568
00:31:21,440 --> 00:31:22,640
Not simple like that.

569
00:31:23,680 --> 00:31:25,210
Go home and have a good rest.

570
00:31:25,600 --> 00:31:26,280
Bye.

571
00:31:26,400 --> 00:31:27,200
Bye.

572
00:32:06,640 --> 00:32:07,560
Ms. Oda.

573
00:33:36,200 --> 00:33:36,930
Let's start.

574
00:34:10,239 --> 00:34:11,800
Ms. Oda.

575
00:34:18,679 --> 00:34:20,760
What do you mean by this?

576
00:34:23,120 --> 00:34:24,650
I've done it so thoroughly.

577
00:34:25,320 --> 00:34:27,580
Haven't you understood what I meant yet?

578
00:34:35,600 --> 00:34:36,920
My father meant that

579
00:34:37,679 --> 00:34:40,120
I took over everything here.

580
00:34:40,719 --> 00:34:43,320
You and your family should go back to Japan now.

581
00:34:44,469 --> 00:34:46,130
This letter is from my father.

582
00:34:46,280 --> 00:34:48,340
You can read it if you are interested.

583
00:34:49,480 --> 00:34:51,040
And the tickets are ready,

584
00:34:51,320 --> 00:34:52,650
you can leave tomorrow.

585
00:34:52,719 --> 00:34:54,040
How could you?

586
00:34:55,080 --> 00:34:58,640
I have established everything here.

587
00:34:59,520 --> 00:35:00,920
Without me,

588
00:35:01,240 --> 00:35:04,200
the place will be still under Russian control.

589
00:35:05,560 --> 00:35:06,640
What are you?

590
00:35:13,200 --> 00:35:15,000
I'll go find General Kawajima

591
00:35:15,880 --> 00:35:17,120
